data.name: description.Text
data.value: A captivating floral boxed design that can transform your Christmas into a winter wonderland. Our latest White Christmas box combines an arrangement of Green Mini Murrayas, White Cotton Flowers and White Button Poms. Gift this to your loved ones as a symbol of purity and spirit of the season.

data.name: description2.Text
data.value: When words fail, express your love with flowers. Let your significant other know the depths of your devotion with this enchanting mini bouquet, featuring stunning blooms such as pink roses and a pink lily. Have it delivered to their doorstep today as a surprise that will make them love you even more!

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: A dainty and ethereal box full of blooms. Surprise your loved one with a stunning arrangement perfect for any celebration! These blooms are specially handcrafted and placed in a premium box for that luxurious touch.
